{"tid":1560543,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[榮光革命] 連鄰囯都支持我地 今鋪真係冇得輸","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T17:08:31.000Z","uid":107157,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5357a7a8868ceab8db2953258caaa099142adb50","tid":1560543,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=06d295be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">睇下下面啲留言，連鄰囯都感動到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLVmboU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLVmboU.jpg&h=1f4d02e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PCEYX3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPCEYX3V.jpg&h=f7f7618b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪開始要做下we connect，<br />\n將精神係鄰國spread出去，<br />\n<br />\n音樂既力量大家親身感受到，<br />\n果種雞皮，自動流落既眼淚，<br />\n聽完想即刻跟住唱既衝動，<br />\n對「愛國」一詞既改觀。<br />\n<br />\n以前認為「愛國」係無知，白痴，<br />\n望住所有其他國家既人唱國歌唱到喊晒口，覺得佢地好虛偽。<br />\n<br />\n之所以有咁既感覺，就係因為我地缺乏左一樣野。<br />\n<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歸屬感</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n榮光一出，成個價值觀改晒。<br />\n我地要將呢個精神spread出去，<br />\n光復呢個香港，黎個音樂革命 !<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n我地要擴大戰線<br />\n將文宣進擊，攻入鄰國 !<br />\n現實就玩無人機加喇叭，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣新戰線<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">榮光革命</span></span></span></div><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">榮光革命!!!</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"69246298cbe